summary: An Ordinance establishing the curb grades on Evanston Avenue from Ewing Street to Kilbourne Street, on Blewett Street and West Blewett Street, from West Ewing Street to Leary Avenue as established by Ordinance No. 21303; on 1st Avenue Northwest, from Blewett street to Kilbourne Street; and on Phinney Avenue, from Ewing Street to Kilbourne Street, all in the City of Seattle.
